reviewText: This is a really good low impact aerobic workout that can be done in either high intensity or low intensity.  The three instructors that lead the class are motivated, clear with the instructions and the moves are easy to follow.  Great workout for a beginner or the seasoned fitness nut.
Title: Jane Fonda's Personal Trainer Series: Low Impact Aerobics & Stretch VHS

reviewText: I use this video in combination with the other two videos in the Personal Trainer series. This is an excellent workout for a beginner and it's short, so you don't get discouraged. The aerobic moves are easy to learn. The  stretch segment is also well done, although it some of the stretches should  probably be held longer.
Title: Jane Fonda's Personal Trainer Series: Low Impact Aerobics & Stretch VHS

reviewText: If you don't pick up routines easily, this one will probably frustrate  you. I happen to like the aerobics routine very much, but I used to be a  professional (singer/dancer/actress). For me, it is fun! If dancing comes  easily to you and you need a good beginner video, this is a good short  routine (only 13 minutes aerobic). It could also be used as a warm up for a  toning workout by more advanced beginners and intermediates (since there  are both low and mixed impact versions of the routine demonstrated). The  stretch routine is not my favorite. I think Jane did much better in other  videos.
Title: Jane Fonda's Personal Trainer Series: Low Impact Aerobics & Stretch VHS

reviewText: okay if you don't have a lot of time but want to do something, it is not real hard so more for beginners
Title: Jane Fonda's Personal Trainer Series: Low Impact Aerobics & Stretch VHS

reviewText: Holy Cow!  I felt like a cow trying to follow.  If you can do the aerobic section of this tape you are a better person than me.  Watched it several times, tried it a few and got so frustrated that I gave up.  On the other hand, or foot, the stretching is very good and probably worth the price of the tape.  I suggest you borrow a copy before you buy if possible.
summary: Professional dancers might be able to follow.
Title: Jane Fonda's Personal Trainer Series: Low Impact Aerobics & Stretch VHS
